	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Are you sure that PAL Battletoads came first?  Gamefaqs and Wikipedia claim that it was released in early 1993 in Europe, but the copyright date in-game says 1991.  If anything, I think the PAL version of Battletoads is a port of the NTSC version to reduce or eliminate the blank lines.
<br />PAL Battletoads also still uses the same exact unrolled display update code.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
